<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"--><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/n7-mcnn/7bcc9724adf7b803/uploads/2024/10/Close-up-of-shraddha-on-ECMO_16x9-1024x576.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-395836" srcset="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/n7-mcnn/7bcc9724adf7b803/uploads/2024/10/Close-up-of-shraddha-on-ECMO_16x9-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/n7-mcnn/7bcc9724adf7b803/uploads/2024/10/Close-up-of-shraddha-on-ECMO_16x9-300x169.jpg 300w, https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/n7-mcnn/7bcc9724adf7b803/uploads/2024/10/Close-up-of-shraddha-on-ECMO_16x9-768x432.jpg 768w, https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/n7-mcnn/7bcc9724adf7b803/uploads/2024/10/Close-up-of-shraddha-on-ECMO_16x9-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/n7-mcnn/7bcc9724adf7b803/uploads/2024/10/Close-up-of-shraddha-on-ECMO_16x9-2048x1152.jpg 2048w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"><strong><mark style="background-color:#ffffff" class="has-inline-color has-black-color">Shraddha Kaltgutar at Mayo Clinic in Phoenix, AZ</mark></strong></figcaption>



<p>At 27 years old, Shraddha Kalgutkar was told she had less than a year to live. Determined to prove everyone wrong, she turned to <a href="https://www.mayoclinic.org/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Mayo Clinic</a> in Arizona.</p>



<p>Now Shraddha is living proof of the power of innovation combined with a patient's will to survive.</p>



<p><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LlFER2E3OEo" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><strong>Watch: Harnessing the power of innovation and a patient's will to survive</strong></a></p>



